  "longBusinessSummary": "Yduqs Participa\u00e7\u00f5es S.A. provides higher education services in Brazil. The company offers face-to-face, semi-face-to-face, and distance education. It also operates two edtechs to prepare the candidates for exams and competitions named HardWork Medicina and Grupo Q, which offers Qconcursos solutions. It serves under Est\u00e1cio, Ibmec, IDOMED, Wyden, and Dam\u00e1sio brand names. The company was formerly known as Est\u00e1cio Participa\u00e7\u00f5es S.A. Yduqs Participa\u00e7\u00f5es S.A. was founded in 1970 and is headquartered in Rio De Janeiro, Brazil.",
